tor": "\n", "text": "Public Works Commission Meeting 06-23-21 Item 4.A.\n\nPublic Works Commission Agenda Report\n\nTo: Chair Merrick and Members of the Public Works Commission Prepared by: Troy Spayd, Assistant Public Works Director/City Engineer Approved by: Rob DuBoux, Public Works Director/City Engineer Date prepared:   June 17, 2021 Meeting date: June 23, 2021 Subject: Capital Improvement Projects and Disaster Recovery Projects Status Report", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 425, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "3689fe2b-6200-40b6-9eff-6e057cc4e1d9": {"__data__": {"id_": "3689fe2b-6200-40b6-9eff-6e057cc4e1d9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "2c26a387-a9aa-4373-9403-8776ff62620a", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a1e16989489287cf639397516a570a50c68ddd63f9d573066291ace315e41caf", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "855df7af-6be9-4b1f-b9f5-423199f3aaef", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a54497c0bc78a25aff485d3f1b8be1cf3856ee314f27a9e5c8928f1796b3fb21", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "RECOMMENDED ACTION: Receive and file report on the status of the City\u2019s current and upcoming Capital Improvements Projects and Disaster Recovery Projects.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 428, "end_char_idx": 582, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "855df7af-6be9-4b1f-b9f5-423199f3aaef": {"__data__": {"id_": "855df7af-6be9-4b1f-b9f5-423199f3aaef", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "3689fe2b-6200-40b6-9eff-6e057cc4e1d9", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8835ec7e785852706442ce811490db3d5dfdedaf8aa83ce2733567a9fe754f98", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "5cfd3e71-5792-47d9-be4c-e63b76f4eb1b", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7149ff6ac8a54406ea6037d11c1df4bae89be82e8f5b312752e9bf926ce904d2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "DISCUSSION:  Staff will provide a status update on the following active projects in the Fiscal Year 2020-2021 Capital Improvement Program:\n\nCapital Improvement Projects (Design)\n\nMarie Canyon Green Streets\n\n\u00be Updates:\n\n \u0083 The  City  has  recently  received  Measure  W  funds  to  complete  this project.    Staff  is  working  on  the  project  plans  to  prepare  for  public bidding.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 583, "end_char_idx": 969, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "5cfd3e71-5792-47d9-be4c-e63b76f4eb1b": {"__data__": {"id_": "5cfd3e71-5792-47d9-be4c-e63b76f4eb1b", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "855df7af-6be9-4b1f-b9f5-423199f3aaef", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a54497c0bc78a25aff485d3f1b8be1cf3856ee314f27a9e5c8928f1796b3fb21", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "683e3312-97c5-4b31-b79c-27ed38ffe7a4", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9e5e72eb0c00f578ec7b90f51aac5dc02e47b633d03e2fd5d5c523debc778e12", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u00be Project Schedule:\n\n\u0083 Complete Design: August 2021 \u0083 Begin Construction: Winter 2021\n\nPCH Median Improvements Project\n\nPCH Median Improvements Project \u00be Updates:\n\n \u0083 Consultant is working on the final design changes. In July, the City will be  seeking  proposals  from  consultants  to  perform  construction management.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 970, "end_char_idx": 1291, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "683e3312-97c5-4b31-b79c-27ed38ffe7a4": {"__data__": {"id_": "683e3312-97c5-4b31-b79c-27ed38ffe7a4", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "5cfd3e71-5792-47d9-be4c-e63b76f4eb1b", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7149ff6ac8a54406ea6037d11c1df4bae89be82e8f5b312752e9bf926ce904d2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "0723a668-045a-40b7-a214-5dc5a80775ec", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9a1c215136ff3efecb00a4a39f8e54cbaa03a8e69503ea1f78b994f1c93dd6d8", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u00be\n\nProject Schedule: \u0083 Complete Design: late Summer 2021 \u0083 Begin Construction:\n\n Winter 2021\nPage 1 of 6\nAgenda Item # 4.A.\n\nPCH Signal Synchronization System Improvements Project\n\n\u00be Updates:\n\nUpdates:\n\n \u0083 65% design package was submitted to Caltrans in November 2020 and\nwe received comments to those plans.\n\n\u0083 Consultant submitted 95% design documents on Friday June 18, 2021.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1293, "end_char_idx": 1671, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0723a668-045a-40b7-a214-5dc5a80775ec": {"__data__": {"id_": "0723a668-045a-40b7-a214-5dc5a80775ec", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "683e3312-97c5-4b31-b79c-27ed38ffe7a4", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9e5e72eb0c00f578ec7b90f51aac5dc02e47b633d03e2fd5d5c523debc778e12", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "e664e272-78e7-4018-b045-3eaa247e8745", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d338cc0fa26d77b7ee75a05e1337ff43256d576ec5ef2f6d393da7bd896a3169", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u00be\n\nProject Schedule:\n\n\u0083 Complete Final Design: August 2021 \u0083 Advertise:\n\n September 2021 \u0083 Award Contract and Begin Construction: Fall 2021\n\nCivic Center Stormwater Diversion Structure\n\n\u00be Updates:\n\n\u0083 A  Los  Angeles  County  Flood  Control  maintenance  agreement  is required for this project.\n\n  Staff received the County\u2019s approval of the agreement.\n\n\u00be Project Schedule: \u0083 Final Design: Completed.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1673, "end_char_idx": 2073, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e664e272-78e7-4018-b045-3eaa247e8745": {"__data__": {"id_": "e664e272-78e7-4018-b045-3eaa247e8745", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0723a668-045a-40b7-a214-5dc5a80775ec", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9a1c215136ff3efecb00a4a39f8e54cbaa03a8e69503ea1f78b994f1c93dd6d8", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "f7cfbd67-d06d-4a6e-ba0b-1dfd4c032e48", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9321d61a75198d8acd47730e355fb041370442ee0f6b31b19c7b726471566204", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Need approved maintenance agreement to be signed and executed.\n\n\u0083 Begin Construction: Estimated Summer 2021\n\nWestward Beach Road Improvements Project\n\n\u00be Updates:\n\nUpdates:\n\n \u0083 The  project  requires  coordination  with  Los  Angeles  County  Beaches and Harbor.  Staff is working out the final details of the project with the County and will be finalizing the design.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2076, "end_char_idx": 2443, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "f7cfbd67-d06d-4a6e-ba0b-1dfd4c032e48": {"__data__": {"id_": "f7cfbd67-d06d-4a6e-ba0b-1dfd4c032e48", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "e664e272-78e7-4018-b045-3eaa247e8745", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d338cc0fa26d77b7ee75a05e1337ff43256d576ec5ef2f6d393da7bd896a3169", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "217fd2f9-b1db-40ad-af60-23584c132d1c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9812137493d4b6bb97a7612148079a75ccb44f0ce7c6814b3e5fb043947091ef", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u00be Project Schedule:\n\n\u0083 Complete Design: Spring 2021\n\n\u0083 Begin Construction: Fall 2021\n\nCivic Center Water Treatment Facility Phase 2\n\n\u00be Updates:\n\n\u0083 Project is at the 65% design phase.\n\n\u0083 The  City  obtained  a  project  CDP  from  Planning  Commission  on February 1,\n\n 2021.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2445, "end_char_idx": 2719, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "217fd2f9-b1db-40ad-af60-23584c132d1c": {"__data__": {"id_": "217fd2f9-b1db-40ad-af60-23584c132d1c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "f7cfbd67-d06d-4a6e-ba0b-1dfd4c032e48", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9321d61a75198d8acd47730e355fb041370442ee0f6b31b19c7b726471566204", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "cce410c1-c2c8-4c64-b94d-be5ecf554f9a", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8df9ebd5fd4ee54cad1e6e288c7aa84f1a11572bc83437d99145169134453e5a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u0083 The  State  is  reviewing  the  City\u2019s  application  for  the  State  Revolving Fund program.\n\n \u0083 The project assessment engineer has begun the process of evaluating the project costs.\n\n\u0083 Staff hosted the community meeting on May 27, 2021.\n\n\u00be Project Schedule:\n\n\u0083 Complete Design: December 2021 \u0083 Begin Construction: March 2022\n\nPage 2 of 6\nAgenda Item # 4.A.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2721, "end_char_idx": 3082, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "cce410c1-c2c8-4c64-b94d-be5ecf554f9a": {"__data__": {"id_": "cce410c1-c2c8-4c64-b94d-be5ecf554f9a", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "217fd2f9-b1db-40ad-af60-23584c132d1c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9812137493d4b6bb97a7612148079a75ccb44f0ce7c6814b3e5fb043947091ef", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "6e62f01c-b043-45f3-9b2d-3e99659cb868", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8fb224170298b063eada4805746d3badd30ad5b411e7b22fafa31669c991ee67", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Capital Improvement Projects (Construction)\n\nCity Hall Roof Replacement\n\n\u00be Updates:\n\n  The  contractor  continues  to  make  great  progress  and  expects  to complete the project within the next two weeks. City staff is currently working on  a  final  punch  list  and  coordinating  a  site  walk  with  the  manufacturer\u2019s representative.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3084, "end_char_idx": 3425, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "6e62f01c-b043-45f3-9b2d-3e99659cb868": {"__data__": {"id_": "6e62f01c-b043-45f3-9b2d-3e99659cb868", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "cce410c1-c2c8-4c64-b94d-be5ecf554f9a", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8df9ebd5fd4ee54cad1e6e288c7aa84f1a11572bc83437d99145169134453e5a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "79ba6b9c-8fa6-4bdf-ad10-9e93c7806260", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "be93f705a8c4c9159c877a441204b56707fd02459f87fda6354c78594d49f513", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u00be Project Schedule: Estimated completion is June 2021\n\nBluffs Park Workout Station\n\n\u00be Updates: The project has been completed.\n\n Staff continues to work with the contractor for the necessary documentation for final acceptance.\n\nCivic Center Way Improvements\n\n\u00be Updates:\n\n The contractor continues to work on the remaining punch list items and maintain the new planting material. All remaining items are expected to be completed by the end of the month. Civic Center Way remains open to the public.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3427, "end_char_idx": 3924, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "79ba6b9c-8fa6-4bdf-ad10-9e93c7806260": {"__data__": {"id_": "79ba6b9c-8fa6-4bdf-ad10-9e93c7806260", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "6e62f01c-b043-45f3-9b2d-3e99659cb868", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8fb224170298b063eada4805746d3badd30ad