pe  II slurry seal, speed humps and new thermoplastic striping. \u00be Project Schedule:\n\n\u0083 Bids were received on June 10 th .", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4169, "end_char_idx": 4568, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "41b1e46f-983a-427b-962c-c2f54ef3fb6a": {"__data__": {"id_": "41b1e46f-983a-427b-962c-c2f54ef3fb6a", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "51c45098-d003-4cc5-bce1-4808b62c76b0", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a575e6dbd1ee44f6a071972a3f0e43e7acfec82785a81d633fb4d3e0c9f0120e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "031c0c4d-09b9-4efd-8cca-5e1957c9d0da", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "98026a9915d3027575d87ec93d40be95e8e729d18d8f802439092b0c9e7ac598", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Staff is currently reviewing the bids and verifying that they comply with the project specifications.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4571, "end_char_idx": 4672, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "031c0c4d-09b9-4efd-8cca-5e1957c9d0da": {"__data__": {"id_": "031c0c4d-09b9-4efd-8cca-5e1957c9d0da", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "e823ee32-181f-4f48-a3e5-49e477087d22", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a818b63515b498dd8936a3aaabe94c1239af084b8446c19a30a8bb1b8eafdb04", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "41b1e46f-983a-427b-962c-c2f